      <title>葡萄牙反对党领袖要求总理就预算问题“认真谈判”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/portugal-s-opposition-leader-tells-premier-to-negotiate-seriously-on-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙总理路易斯·蒙特内哥罗的中右翼少数派政府如果希望获得议会支持该计划，就必须愿意就 2025 年预算提案做出妥协，社会党反对派领导人佩德罗·努诺·桑托斯如是说。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/portugal-s-opposition-leader-tells-premier-to-negotiate-seriously-on-budget</guid>
